[h1]Respawn Point Tool[/h1]

[b]Version:[/b] v2.0.0

Set your own respawn spots anywhere you can reach with the Toolgun.

Place one respawn point for a simple checkpoint, or place several and respawn at a random one each time. Great for building, sandbox bases, events, PvP setups, obstacle courses, or just messing around.

Fully multiplayer compatible: every player gets their own personal respawn points.

[h2]Features[/h2]
[list]
[*]Personal respawn points for each player
[*]Multiple respawn points with random respawns
[*]Respawn facing direction is saved
[*]Optional saved spawns per map
[*]Visible marker while holding the tool
[*]Placement preview before you click
[*]Optional danger check for nearby NPCs and NextBots
[*]HUD count while holding the tool
[*]Easy remove and clear controls
[/list]

[h2]Controls[/h2]
[list]
[*]Left-click: add a respawn point
[*]Right-click: remove the aimed respawn point
[*]Reload: clear your respawn points on the current map
[/list]

Find it in the Toolgun menu under [b]Respawn Point Tool[/b].
